# Cursor kit bootstrap

This project uses **cursor-kit** (shared rules + skills) and optionally **mattpocock/skills**.

## Automatic bootstrap

New projects are bootstrapped by the **workspaceOpen hook** (`~/.cursor/hooks/`): rules and `project-setup.json` are copied when you open a folder in Cursor. Manual bootstrap: `~/cursor-kit/scripts/bootstrap-project.sh .`

## First session — Matt Pocock (blocking)

Read `.cursor/project-setup.json` **before every reply**. If `mattPocockSetup` is false, **`matt-pocock-setup-pending.mdc` takes priority** over all other work until setup completes or the user explicitly skips.

## Always apply in this project

| Task | Use |
|------|-----|
| Any `.css` edit | **`responsive-css`** skill (mandatory) |
| PHP / asset changes | **`asset-violation-protocol`** rule |
| Missing data / config | **`fail-fast`** rule — no invented defaults |
| New feature / bug | Matt Pocock: `/grill-with-docs`, `/diagnose` when appropriate (**not** `/tdd` — see **`no-tdd`**) |
| Plans | **`research-confirmed-plans`** — verify before speculative options |

## Skills location

Skills install globally to `~/.cursor/skills/` via `npx skills add`. Project rules live in `.cursor/rules/`.
